# Firebase admin / FCM service-account secret. Used by the backend to send
# push, NOT needed in the driver app repo at all — but if it ends up here
# during local experiments, never commit it. (google-services.json IS
# public client config and is kept in-tree for EAS builds.)
fcm-service-account.json

